{"tid":747626,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖慎入) 1866年，英國參贊向中國總理衙門提出建議停止凌遲...","createTime":"2018-07-18T13:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T16:42:35.000Z","uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e7f8b1917ea9edcc439bde77a4ca415c9ef4bae","tid":747626,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:40:44.000Z","msg":"1866年，英國參贊威妥瑪向中國總理衙門提出建議，停止凌遲這種極度野蠻、不人道的刑罰，但清政府只允許對洋人交付的犯人免用凌遲；直到1905年，在各國的外交壓力之下，光緒帝才勉強同意不再對中國人使用凌遲、梟首等酷刑&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213553_d00a4d638abcdab7da7a2dc2677e794f.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F213553_d00a4d638abcdab7da7a2dc2677e794f.png&d=qask72%2FD4s3iSAoRDr6ZG5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=10f3cb38\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213553_d00a4d638abcdab7da7a2dc2677e794f.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213821_afef428d8d5ae3d5c6c24379128b129f.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F213821_afef428d8d5ae3d5c6c24379128b129f.png&d=qask72%2FD4s3iSAoRDr6ZG5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=280e91f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213821_afef428d8d5ae3d5c6c24379128b129f.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213554_a0bb50de0019230791e6f44e7b642e3e.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F213554_a0bb50de0019230791e6f44e7b642e3e.png&d=qask72%2FD4s3iSAoRDr6ZG5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=77e5195a\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213554_a0bb50de0019230791e6f44e7b642e3e.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213554_315c1fb3e765a3619c5370522c15a48e.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F213554_315c1fb3e765a3619c5370522c15a48e.png&d=qask72%2FD4s3iSAoRDr6ZG5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=a04fc3d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213554_315c1fb3e765a3619c5370522c15a48e.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213555_315c1fb3e765a3619c5370522c15a48e.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F213555_315c1fb3e765a3619c5370522c15a48e.png&d=qask72%2FD4s3iSAoRDr6ZG5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=3afbf1bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/213555_315c1fb3e765a3619c5370522c15a48e.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>威妥瑪（英語：Sir Thomas Francis Wade；威妥瑪拼音：Wei1 Tʻo3-ma3）；1818年8月25日－1895年7月31日），全名湯瑪斯&middot;法蘭西斯&middot;韋德，是19世紀的英國外交家與漢學家，曾在中國生活四十餘年。1869年至1882年任英國駐華全權公使。1888年，任劍橋大學首位漢學教授。曾榮獲聖米迦勒及聖佐治勳章及巴斯勳章。<br />\n威妥瑪與翟理斯創造了一套用於拼寫中文普通話的羅馬拼音系統，即威妥瑪拼音。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c2f7eebacae1ab0b19c04ae74ef079cce211316c","tid":747626,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37054217427384ad29e090c5227b6a9aae1312be","tid":747626,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 殘酷帝國"},{"pid":"75c97855e9510585b39ce51ebfc1883b51c324af","tid":747626,"uid":30991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"唔敢睇圖 自己Wiki左 <br />\n睇字都已經好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30d444b9131f6cbffd4dd4f83159b91ed5b